This gives us the equation
\[\left(\begin{pmatrix} 2 + 7t \\ -3 + 5t \\ -3 - t \end{pmatrix} - \begin{pmatrix} 4 \\ 4 \\ 5 \end{pmatrix} \right) \cdot \begin{pmatrix} 7 \\ 5 \\ -1 \end{pmatrix} = 0.\]Then
