Problem: Find the volume of the region given by the inequality
\[|x + y + z| + |x + y - z| + |x - y + z| + |-x + y + z| \le 4.\]
Let's think step by step: Let
\[f(x,y,z) = |x + y + z| + |x + y - z| + |x - y + z| + |-x + y + z|.\]Note that
\begin{align*}
f(-x,y,z) &= |-x + y + z| + |-x + y - z| + |-x - y + z| + |x + y + z| \\
